text.en:
Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each effect of "Hecahands Tartarus" once per turn);
● If you control a "Hecahands" monster: Target 1 Spell/Trap your opponent controls; return it to the hand.
● Fusion Summon 1 "Hecahands" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, by banishing its materials from your field and/or GY. If you use a face-up monster(s) you control owned by your opponent, you can treat it as a "Hecahands" monster.
